					<div class="bio">
						<h4>Ryan Byrnes</h4>
												<p>Ryan Byrnes is a book editor at <em>Springer Nature</em>. His first novel, <em>Royal Beauty Bright</em>, won an Independent Publisher Book Award while his second novel, <em>My Dear Antonio</em>, was published in 2024. His writing has also appeared in <em>New York Journal of Books</em>, <em>Italian America</em>, <em>December</em>, <em>Pembroke</em>, and more. He lives in Brooklyn. As a young writer beginning his career, he hopes to continue learning the craft and helping others tell their stories.</p>
